  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight for your rights as a homeless and use the invisibility skills you have.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be fast, be the best and get back your liberty in a brand new and fun experience full of hostile robots and danger.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344410/extras/dfef34a4d26bc9b4c3284fcc7893221e.avif?t=1734103548\" width=616 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game is a SPEEDRUNNER and mini Metroidvania in two parts.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Improve your tactic, find new shortcuts to complete the map in your best time possible.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use frequently many powerful weapons or play it in a more \"stealthy\" way, it's up to you!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>. REPLAYABILITY: beat your own record!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>. huge maps full of secrets</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>. tons of robotic enemies</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dont give up and use what you have:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>. your magic crutch</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>. your hat to make high jumps and to become invisibile </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>...and even </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>. wall jumps</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>. 360° shooting</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>. unlimited ammo to choose: nails, granates, plasma, electricity, acid...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>. collecting plastic bottles and things of value</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>. ground pounding </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Art as game</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A cute funny platformer for the player with sense of justice!</strong></p>",
